subproject.description:
Project objectives:
- to strengthen the implementation of UN Cares Programme, 
- to enhance the national capacity for strategic planning, costing and budgeting, and M&E, 
- to support activities aiming at reducing stigma and discrimination and promoting gender and human rights of PLWH.
subproject.title: UN Joint Advocacy Proj on HIV

subproject.corporate outcome: Strengthened national capacities for implementation of HIV funds and programmes, including those financed through multilateral initiatives like the Global Fund to fight AIDS, Tuberculosis, and Malaria
